-- Jobs Says Apple to Give All IPhone 4 Users a Bumper Case to Aid Reception
-- Greg Chang
-- 2010-07-16T17:31:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-16/jobs-says-apple-to-give-all-iphone-4-users-a-bumper-case-to-aid-reception.html

          
          
             Apple Inc. plans to give a bumper
case to every iPhone 4 user, Chief Executive Steve Jobs told
reporters today. The company has sold more than 3 million units
of the model. Every user who previously bought a bumper will get
a refund.  
          
          


  


        